##############################################
#
#  README for audio file reader with FFMPEG
#
##############################################

Use: "make"
to compile.
The implemented command line is: g++ ffmp.cpp -o ffmp -std=c++11 -lavutil -lavcodec -lavformat -L/usr/local/lib 

Use: "make clean"
to clean the previous compilation.


test.wav and test.mp3 are the similar but in different format.  


-------------- PLEASE PAY ATTENTION ON THIS -------

This version has been tested on Linux OS (Ubuntu) with: 
libavutil.so.51
libavcodec.so.53
libavformat.so.53
